'''[[Softball]]''' at the '''[[2010 Asian Games]]''' was held in [[Guangzhou]], [[Guangdong]], [[People's Republic of China|China]] from November 19 to 26, 2010. Only a women's competition was held. All games were played at the [[Tianhe Softball Field]].
{{TOCLimit|3}}
